arStrings.szText: "The spirits look to have been freed."
Yes, (deep breath) I believe so. The paladins are finally at peace. I could not have done this alone. The Light shines bright within you.
Tired, but still full of spirit.
I must return to Zarbinzet. I shall tell the other Zakarum of Carthas and the paladins who gave their lives to contain Mephisto's corruption.
May the Light guide your way.
